snippet.title: 3.3 Version PV - Cyberangel - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
"Following your trail, I dove deep into the lost world to bring you home." Having acquired the Herrscher Core from the Sea of Quanta, Bronya is returning as the Herrscher of Reason!

No better way to spend the summer on an uncharted island full of unreal encounters~ Odd Drifter is coming with free summer outfits for HoV, Swallowtail Phantasm & Stalker: Phantom Iron!

Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB
